                    	<note xml:id="n_dating" type="dating">
                    	    
<p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">Like <ref target="let729.xml">letter 729</ref> to Theo, this letter was written on Friday, 4 January 1889. This was, after all, the day of Vincent’s ‘first trip out of the hospital’ <ref target="#l-2">(ll. 2-3)</ref>. <ref target="let729.xml">See letter 729</ref>, <hi rend="italics">Date</hi>.</p>
                    	</note>
                    
                    
                    
                    	<note xml:id="n_remarks" type="remarks">
                    	    
                                    
<p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">Written in pencil on the back of <ref target="let729.xml">letter 729</ref> to Theo. It is not certain whether Theo let Gauguin read the letter in this form or whether he made a copy for him.</p>
                                    
                                
                    	</note>
                    
